Rules:

HA gun combined with AA director (10cm+Director, 12.7cm+Director) counts as either HA gun or HA_with_Director, but not AA director

Activation priority:

Single ship:  API 1 > 2,3,5,8    API4>6, API5>8, API7>9 API 10>8,9,11,12  API11 > 9

Multiple ship in one fleet:  Higher Api value have trigger priority

Example:

You have a maya with API10, a mitsuki with API9 and Akizuki with API1 in a fleet.

In air phase, you first roll for API10, if fail then roll API9.  That that fails, you roll for API1.

---

Practical applications:  Do not fit a low strength AACI (eg. API9) to go with Akizuki
